import React from 'react'; import './WorkoutTemplate.css'; const WorkoutTemplate = ({ onDelete, workout_id, name, day_type, plan_type, difficulty_level, exercises }) => { return (

{name}

Day Type

{exercises.map(exercise => exercise.exercise_name).join(', ')}
